Subtotaling your reports gives you a tool to analyze trends in the data. You can group sets of information, sort the groupings, and compare subtotals for each set against the overall total.

To subtotal report results: 
Enhanced Folder Sharing
Create and Customize Reports
Report Builder

Click Customize or Edit from any report.
In the report builder, add a summary field to the report.
Summaries show up at grouping levels as well as for individual rows.
